snippet.title: How to find Baltic amber in the Baltic sea - Amberhunting
snippet.description:
#amberhunting #fossilhunting #balticamber
Lockdown got lifted!  And the first weekend after we went to the baltic sea with hopes to hunt for some baltic amber and fossils. In the end did succed to find some, as well as some fossils. Super satisfying weekend, felt alive again after being locked in my city ^^

Sound from Zapsplat.com
